  <chapter id="install">
    <title>Installation of VISHNU</title>
    <section>
      <title>Requirements</title>
      <para>VISHNU can be installed on Linux systems only (preferably Debian distributions), and requires the following software:</para>
      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Boost C++ libraries (1.45 or greater)</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>OmniORB (4.1.4 or greater)</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>EMF4CPP (0.0.2 patched - see debian packages below - or greater)</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>SSH</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>PostGreSQL (8.0 or greater) or MySQL (5.0 or greater)</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>Sysfera-DS (DIET version 2.7 minimum + le module log service associé)</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>On all hosts providing task mgmt services (TMS module):</para>
          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>Torque API v3.2.6</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>IBM LoadLeveler API</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>OR SLURM API v2.2.1</para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </section>
